WEBVTT

00:00.520 --> 00:01.040
Your son

00:01.360 --> 00:02.560
Is willing to bear this heavy responsibility

00:02.880 --> 00:03.720
Ridiculous

00:04.160 --> 00:05.960
You're just a prince

00:06.080 --> 00:07.640
Haven't even fought many battles

00:07.880 --> 00:09.280
What reason and ability do you have

00:09.360 --> 00:10.960
To bear the responsibility for defeat?
